// MSP_OSD_CONFIG (MSPv1)
// Retrieves OSD configuration settings and layout for screen 0. Coordinates are packed as `(Y << 8) | X`. When `USE_OSD` is not compiled in, only `osdDriverType` = `OSD_DRIVER_NONE` is returned.
